CoffeeCup Live Chat 6.0 - Live Chat with Users on your Website!

Full Retail Version - NOT A TRIAL

Live Chat 6.0
Released: May 1, 2006

This program allows visitors the opportunity to chat with you in real time by just clicking on a chat link from your website. Live Chat is a great way to have support on your Website or to talk to people that are visiting your Website live.

Enjoy!
